Installation:

Possibly turn ssl verification off

git config --global http.sslVerify false

Clone repo

git clone git://github.com/trumanellis/Vim-Config.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

